      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;We have done this quest twice now and hte pet trick works great. We did it with the Druid summoned pet.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;For those who do not know the &amp;quot;Pet Method&amp;quot; here it is in a nut shell.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Somehow get a pet, kill the two giants at the foot of the ramp leading to Kael. Put the pet at the top right corner of the ramp and set it to guard. It should poin in the direction of the lost dwarf. If you stand infront of your pet (facing your pet) and walk backward you should &amp;quot;trip&amp;quot; over the dwarf.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Workd for us twice only took a few min to do.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Heracy&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by heracy on &lt;span class="date_text"&gt;04-04-2006&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="time_text"&gt;11:24 AM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
